    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "You have needed to develop greater tenderness and larger sympathy, that you might come close to those in need of gentle, sympathetic, loving words. Your children will call out these traits of character and will help you to develop breadth of mind and judgment. Through loving association with them, you will learn to be more tender and sympathetic in your ministry for suffering humanity.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Lt 329, 1904\" data-link=\"14069.8194001\">Letter 329, 1904</span>.</span></a></sup>",
