    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Sister J should cultivate love and sympathy. She should manifest tender affection for the motherless children under her care. This would be a blessing to these children of God&apos;s love and would be reflected back upon her in affection and love.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"3T 531.2\" data-link=\"119.2497\">Ibid., 3:531, 532</span>.</span></a></sup>",
